<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可怜的杰佩托被关进了监狱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但此时匹诺曹正笑着穿过森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹没有穿衣服，但是他一点儿都不在乎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我自由了，我自由了。”他一边跑一边喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以跑，可以跳，还可以玩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳开始落山了，匹诺曹开始觉得累了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他回到杰佩托的家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我饿了。”他说。他找遍了家里所有的食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56277</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是匹诺曹不知道怎么做饭，所以他没办法吃晚餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好冷。”他说，他找遍了家里所有的衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是在杰佩托给他做衣服之前，他逃跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他只好把自己裹在毯子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我累了。”他说。但是杰佩托的床太高了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”匹诺曹哭道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我又冷又饿又累，还没有人照顾我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大大的泪珠顺着他的木头脸庞滑落。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果不是你，杰佩托现在还在这里。”一个小声音传了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁在那儿？”匹诺曹害怕地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夜幕降临，房间里面越来越黑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹看不到任何人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我。”那个声音再次传来，并伴随着蟋蟀的叫声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>餐桌上的小蜡烛突然亮了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹看到一只蟋蟀从蜡烛上爬了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！是一只虫子！”匹诺曹说，“你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是蟋蟀米克。你可以叫我蟋蟀先生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我住在这个房间里已经有一百年了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我从来没有见过像你这样的坏孩子！”他责骂道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不喜欢你！”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对蟋蟀先生感到很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真没礼貌！”蟋蟀先生叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直在想办法帮助你，而杰佩托一直都是一个善良的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这就是你报答你朋友们的方式吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果是这样，你不会有什么好朋友的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们应该孝敬父母，但是你没有！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹用手拍着桌子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190546</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他试图把蟋蟀先生压扁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190546</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会让你看到！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我可以拥有我想要的所有朋友！”匹诺曹尖叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我可以做我想做的事情！我不用孝敬任何人！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要去冒险。有一天，我会成为又有钱又有名的人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟋蟀先生跳到地板上，想要逃跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是匹诺曹追着他，想要踩扁他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的选择非常错误！”蟋蟀先生说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天，这些错误的选择会伤害到你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你无法逃避你所做的错误的决定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你必须要学会做一个诚实善良的男孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叫着跑向门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会去工作。我也不会去学习。我不会听你说的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我只会做我想做的！”匹诺曹尖声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟋蟀先生跑到了门下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹用力踢了一下门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走到桌子旁边坐下，哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会听你的话，也不会听其他任何人的话。”他哭着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>慢慢地，他就睡着了。泪水挂在他的鼻子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>